{"type":"message","id":"ae75dcb5","parentId":"7ad3655a","timestamp":"2026-04-07T02:57:31.470Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You are running a boot check. Follow BOOT.md instructions exactly.\n\nBOOT.md:\n# 网关重启清单 (Crash Recovery)\n\n由于外部上下文截断或系统重载带来的重新连接，需遵循以下恢复协议：\n1. **镇定与重建**：禁止向用户询问无意义的“上次进行到哪了”，主动查阅 `MEMORY.md` 最新指针、最近的 `task.md` 以及 Git Worktree `git status` 收集未提交的痕迹。\n2. **溯源未竞事务**：排查 `[/]` 进行中状态的事务节点。\n3. **安全确认闭环**：如果不确定远程状态，立即通过 `git fetch` 和分支对比核定自己所在的时间线进度，防止覆盖团队产出。\n4. **恢复宣告**：以高度压缩的信息汇报断点恢复策略：“重启追踪到 XXX 相关变更，现继续执行...”。\n\nIf BOOT.md asks you to send a message, use the message tool (action=send with channel + target).\nUse the `target` field (not `to`) for message tool destinations.\nAfter sending with the message tool, reply with ONLY: NO_REPLY.\nIf nothing needs attention, reply with ONLY: NO_REPLY."}],"timestamp":1775530651444}}
